<title>USA: Scopus sets offering.</title>
<headline>Scopus sets offering.</headline>
<dateline>EMERYVILLE, Calif. 1996-11-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Scopus Technology Inc Wednesday priced its public offering of 2,000,000 shares of stock at $37.50 a share.</p>
<p>Of the total, 1,150,000 shares are offered by the company and 850,000 shares are offered by selling shareholders.</p>
<p>The company said the net proceeds to the company from the offering will be used for general corporate purposes, including working capital. The principal purpose of this offering is to obtain additional capital to fund the growth of the company.</p>
